                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i0">
                     <t:locus xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" from="1v" to="201v">1v-201v</t:locus>
                     <textLang xml:lang="ar">Arabic</textLang>
                     <title type="apodous" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT0049IHA#s39IHA">قران, Second half (ǧuz’ 16-30)</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="ar">
                        <t:locus xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" target="#1v">-1v</t:locus>بسم الله الرحمن الرحيم كهيعص ذكر رحمت ربك عبده زكريا</incipit>
                     <explicit xml:lang="ar">
                        <t:locus xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" target="#201v">-201v</t:locus>خالدين فيها ما دامت السموات والارض الا ما شاء</explicit>
                     <note>The text begins with verse 19:1. On fol. 200v, the beginning of sura 86. Fol. 201 belongs to the first half of al-Qur’ān containing text from sūra 11. Fol. 57 is loose and placed wrong: it contains text from sūra 89 and should be placed after fol. 200. Words divided into two lines. Vocalized.</note>
                     <note/>
                  </msItem>
